{"tid":1798430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[關於港獨] 阻你十秒入嚟睇睇，極緊要，影響成場運動","createTime":"2019-12-26T08:10:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T09:29:22.000Z","uid":89898,"like":12,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3b6cce1d0b1784bf53fea88b458c1d2b0212d158","tid":1798430,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T08:10:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>「回應五大訴求，否則推動獨立」 <br />\n「Five demands, or indie」</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n理解唔少人，尤其後生一輩其實好堅定想要獨；但係都唔少傳統中老年嘅有大中華情意結，同埋始終可能有令國際難做嘢嘅考量，所以係時候要叫新口號了。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「回應五大訴求，否則推動獨立」 <br />\n「Five demands, or indie」</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n叫呢set新口號，將會係影響成場運動末來嘅路，主要原因有四：<br />\n<br />\n1) 串連呢半年爭取嘅五大訴求同港獨呢個hidden agenda，唔係直接爭取港獨，但係又raise到個noise。原理同6.9林鄭出嚟話照開會先衝立會一樣，或者<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「和&gt;deadline&gt;勇」公式</span></span>一樣，出師有名。<br />\n<br />\n2) 將港獨思潮嘅冒起歸究於港共漠視民意，面對讓步同港獨，佢哋要跪低落實<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">五大訴求嘅誘因</span></span>大咗，那怕讓嘅只係少少一步，至少係個缺口 ❨雖然唔多睇好❩。<br />\n<br />\n3) 最重要嘅一點，畀到好多想/未想推港獨，但係喺街頭唔敢嗌「香港獨立」嘅手足一個上台階。對未想獨嘅，呢set口號其實只係爭取五大訴求；對想獨嘅，就係爭取獨立，完美<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">化解</span></span>獨派同非獨派嘅<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">矛盾同互相指責</span></span>嘅機會。<br />\n<br />\n4) 長遠而言，就係藉呢個運動將<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">港獨思潮灌輸</span></span>喺每一個人腦入面。7.21到而家，見住大家將「光復香港，時代革命」叫到街知巷聞。講明「革命」呢口號都得，呢兩句冇理由唔得掛。<br />\n<br />\n所以，可唔可以跟我講一次<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「回應五大訴求，否則推動獨立」 <br />\n「Five demands, or indie」</span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"35ea9af32c7a051a508fafbb55a02cddfbc39a2b","tid":1798430,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T08:10:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea497af716ef27158ad1f86945821d7e7af9b968","tid":1798430,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T08:11:13.000Z","msg":"得唔得都求comment吓"},{"pid":"83fb69d5bfa9a7989a59118c0a2617dad11bb11d","tid":1798430,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T08:11:24.000Z","msg":"認同嘅請幫推"},{"pid":"6d0c74de935256d6f992e3a6d36dcd83e84f18d2","tid":1798430,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T08:11:47.000Z","msg":"決定成場運動末來嘅方向"},{"pid":"4d9e96b733fd8d2a5685b9fc453768ff8b750c64","tid":1798430,"uid":205552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T08:12:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c8f6f71d3408d4c0e49e6e2e76c33a3eff013c7","tid":1798430,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T08:12:28.000Z","msg":"利申堅決守護一國兩制<br />\n反對一切分裂國家主權嘅行為"},{"pid":"1608045b6f96ff6bd81f0af2b0f1288063e0c3a1","tid":1798430,"uid":302347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T08:12:30.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"7b205e569de94e90b5ce34864ba364fec03561f3","tid":1798430,"uid":266503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T08:13:13.000Z","msg":"推 出大絕都要儲氣呢"},{"pid":"5d160cf5220a45c7143a4585d4d05891518efc42","tid":1798430,"uid":11549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T08:13:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"45f7e91022df1626411697776a1ebe215773210d","tid":1798430,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T08:13:48.000Z","msg":"唯一draw back係嗌「five demands」會有唔同嘅回應，尤其如果個post推唔到上去冇人識呢句口號的話"},{"pid":"0b497833723eb48f896694b564c5cc2c5375e5cc","tid":1798430,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T08:15:03.000Z","msg":"嗱獨唔獨立嘅決定權就喺你度喇mon post港共走狗"},{"pid":"e23c52ff2943e057042db70add0d84f66878ae08","tid":1798430,"uid":16676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T08:15:51.000Z","msg":"同當日無喇喇改叫「六大訴求, 缺一不」有乜分別<br />\n初心一樣, 無乜必要改<br />\n勿忘初心"},{"pid":"5d918a12f2ee45f2fd13d21f7fb3a7d364167348","tid":1798430,"uid":305536,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T08:16:02.000Z","msg":"以下轉自中國大陸微信，請大家醒醒吧：<br />\n<br />\n「看網友評論：你們香港人顯然不了解中央政府對港獨的定義。<br />\n目前中央政府將只要不跪下做奴才的全都定義為港獨。<br />\n等你們全都跪下了，中央政府會將跪的姿勢不正確的定義為港獨。<br />\n等你們跪下的姿勢都符合要求了，中央政府會將跪著臉上沒有笑容的定義為港獨。<br />\n等你們跪著笑著對時候，中央政府會將心裡沒有全然服從的定義為港獨。<br />\n⋯⋯⋯<br />\n現在香港人明白什麼是港獨的定義了嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n看，還是中國人了解中共吧！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins>應該係中國同美國開始傾第二次貿易戰既時候可以正式吹風</ins>"},{"pid":"d928058413b27cdf463db2a2ba4c826688a79f20","tid":1798430,"uid":89898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T08:16:11.000Z","msg":"認真嘅，想獨都唔可以忽略好多傳統老一輩泛民係政治潔癖大中華膠嘅現實"},{"pid":"ba0f855b38103d6452e322d0a08217c467a0bb8d","tid":1798430,"uid":188685,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T08:17:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">12.29 愛丁堡</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">12.31 和你拖</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1.1  兩點維園見</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">*請準時 勿打尖</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">中環pepe專門店=人血饅頭</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U560vkO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU560vkO.jpg&h=eae2ad0b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wOBGZd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwOBGZd9.jpg&h=56f142bf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JtsrqT9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJtsrqT9.jpg&h=e550811c&s={SIZE}\" /><