>\n以為係 indie rock 呀 (一種流行音樂)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T08:29:45.000Z","msg":"yes之前都係覺得indie就係指音樂嘅indie，但係wiki完話係泛指&quot;independence&quot;呢個字<br />\n<br />\n定真係3-5咁嘅slogan?<br />\n<br />\n定諗過第二句5-5，順便解決叫「five demands」有唔同回應嘅問題？"},{"pid":"63d0a8de115dd32c2f952fd56ca1b006b94a7af4","tid":1798430,"uid":282490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45f7e91022df1626411697776a1ebe215773210d","tid":1798430,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T08:13:48.000Z","msg":"唯一draw back係嗌「five demands」會有唔同嘅回應，尤其如果個post推唔到上去冇人識呢句口號的話"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T08:31:07.000Z","msg":"慢慢教<br />\n<br />\n叫香港人<br />\n<br />\n而家無人回加油<br />\n<br />\n都係叫報仇"}]}